{"tid":1632815,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「10.6一役」請用數分鐘去睇一睇","createTime":"2019-10-06T23:34:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T23:54:09.000Z","uid":127440,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2420e49f08e5b51799428a612fcffa1e07513d8d","tid":1632815,"uid":127440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T23:34:03.000Z","msg":"係10.6呢一個夜晚，唔同既平台都出現緊類近既訊息。<br />\n<br />\n「<span style=\"color: red;\">唔割，但你做錯咗。</span>」<br />\n「<span style=\"color: red;\">同路人，但你做錯咗。</span>」<br />\n「<span style=\"color: red;\">大家係勇武，但你做錯咗。</span>」<br />\n<br />\n但究竟係呢一場運動入面，有咩究竟係岩，有咩究竟係唔岩？<br />\n<br />\n一件事既對錯，每個人都有唔同既睇法，<br />\n以「偷野」為例：<br />\n一般人都知偷野係犯法行為，所以係錯！<br />\n但當你係賊仔，呢件事唔係錯！<br />\n<br />\n一個人去睇一件事既對錯係基於佢既道德底線同直覺，而呢兩野都係與生俱來，無得改變，所以希望大家可以平心去討論呢場運動，激動無問題，係人都會有情緒，但要學識慢慢靜落嚟去理解人哋既意見，奉勸大家一句：「集各家之大成」<br />\n<br />\n其次，<br />\n示威者被人比喻成「<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">曱甴</span></strong>」，我好嬲同時好羞恥......<br />\n因為將一個群組形容為「曱甴」，係製造「去人性化」既仇恨，係為施加暴力甚至殺人合理化以至正義化製造恐怖既藉口。<br />\n所以，我地要謹記，我地唔係「曱甴」，我地係為「自由」而生既人類！<br />\n同時亦要以行動證明自身價值！<br />\n<br />\n第三，<br />\n今日「摩士一戰」，我好嬲但同時好傷感...<br />\n<br />\n原本好多人大叫要跟隊打波，到最後竟然落荒而逃...<br />\n<br />\n「勇武 」一字唔係用黎讚頌一個人既勇氣，記住係一種精神，<br />\n一種<br />\n「無懼、無畏、無私」既心態。<br />\n面對極權，我地要展現出以上精神，<br />\n即使你只係和理非都好......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有，<br />\n「光復香港，時代革命」<br />\n若果你曾經叫過呢個口號，請為呢句口號負責任。<br />\n所以，「撞到狗」、「蒙面法」以及等等既惡法，我地唔需要畏懼！<br />\n當你產生出畏懼亦代表你已經畏懼咗呢一個腐敗既政權。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後送上一張本人一直謹記係心中既圖比大家。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OrhCWjY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOrhCWjY.jpg&h=212325ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#共勉之<br />\n#香港人"},{"pid":"3f7873c903bc34c1418dfbd7c61655607d7bb404","tid":1632815,"uid":127440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T23:34:57.000Z","msg":"自推十連<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"447e4718fa71e48a7004db6c037ec95da07f8f53","tid":1632815,"uid":127440,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T23:35:14.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"42dbfaa10871e0e3022c54feb50f08913eabdaa7","tid":1632815,"uid":127440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T23:35:26.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"c32e4ab9fd972f26754085b09b276693e30c4751","tid":1632815,"uid":127440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T23:36:10.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"2a66536c301fadffdd370f115eb23f869fc4dfd4","tid":1632815,"uid":127440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T23:36:24.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"7cd7fb7c05383a0c5bb584d01f10155686be91a0","tid":1632815,"uid":127440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T23:36:34.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"9ad632638b2cd89989d399f3753582f6b28735c0","tid":1632815,"uid":127440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T23:36:46.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"90b48086d833170ea3f891dce86487d98be2c9a6","tid":1632815,"uid":127440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T23:36:59.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"d35731701fb730624413afde7db1aac0ca60bda5","tid":1632815,"uid":127440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T23:37:11.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"f7237d02667a4d9d61939df5fa1a60eacf42af4f","tid":1632815,"uid":127440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T23:37:22.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"12a52491d70aabf7e5c1cde4dc53e107d9b5223a","tid":1632815,"uid":127440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T23:37:32.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"06baf660c4edc431076ac661de755036f39f7111","tid":1632815,"uid":27146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T23:37:38.000Z","msg":"其實都唔係未試過錯啦，覺得錯咪自我修正，洗地道歉做文宣"},{"pid":"2201acfa9701ce350b0248942d9cddb439512af7","tid":1632815,"uid":225247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T23:39:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/s